# nexus /.end — END engine surface SSOT
# Implements hive raw 90 end-surface-composition-META-witness (FORWARD SPEC, status=new).
# Created 2026-04-27.
#
# raw 90 thesis: END logic is COMPOSITION (not new logic) of 7 component raws + nexus extensions.
# nexus 는 ω-cycle (kick) + atlas-absorb + drill 등 프로젝트-고유 termination event 가 있어,
# generic mapping 위에 nexus-specific extension 을 4개 추가.
#
# Until raw 1 os-lock 가 .end 로 확장될 때까지 advisory.

end-composition 1 new "END as union of 7 component raws (raw 90 META-witness)"
  slug end-composition-canonical
  enforce-layer hive-agent
  enforce-layer-rationale per hive raw 90 — hive-agent META documentation layer; OS-level cannot evaluate semantic composition; lint scans .end for end-composition + end-event-type-mapping fields.

  # 7 component raws — END logic distributed across (inherited from hive raw 90):
  component-raw raw:session-interrupt-recovery               # raw 27 — session-end (graceful + crash recovery)
  component-raw raw:omega-saturation-default                 # raw 39 — cycle-end (default Ω cycle)
  component-raw raw:hard-implementation-default              # raw 43 — cycle-end (limit-witness stop)
  component-raw raw:plan-omega-saturation                    # raw 37 — cycle-end (planning saturation)
  component-raw raw:design-falsifier-retire-rule             # raw 71 — design-end (FALSIFIER condition auto-retire)
  component-raw raw:execution-daemon-singleton-stale-lock-witness  # raw 78 — daemon-end
  component-raw raw:execution-sentinel-result-decoding       # raw 80 — subprocess-end (sentinel string atomic END signal)
  component-raw raw:deploy-staged-publication-state-machine  # raw 83 — artifact-end (published → archived transition)

  why END is the OUTPUT state of the other engines — RAW decays → retired, OWN changes → logged, ROADMAP completes → archived, COMMAND executes → logged, TURN cycles → logged, all end at END via fixpoint-witness binding.
  scope nexus engine-surface enumeration completion (raw 43 7/7)
  proof tool/end_composition_check.hexa (forward)
  proof design/kick/*.json (witness JSON 의 sentinel `__KICK_RESULT__ <PASS|FAIL>` 가 raw 80 binding)
  omega-stop fixpoint-convergence

end-event-type-mapping 1 new "per-event-type → component-raw mapping (nexus-specific extensions)"
  slug end-event-type-mapping-canonical
  enforce-layer hive-agent

  # generic mappings (inherited from hive raw 90):
  map session-end          raw:session-interrupt-recovery               # raw 27
  map cycle-end-fixpoint   raw:omega-saturation-default                 # raw 39
  map cycle-end-limit      raw:hard-implementation-default              # raw 43
  map cycle-end-planning   raw:plan-omega-saturation                    # raw 37
  map design-end           raw:design-falsifier-retire-rule             # raw 71
  map daemon-end           raw:execution-daemon-singleton-stale-lock-witness  # raw 78
  map subprocess-end       raw:execution-sentinel-result-decoding       # raw 80
  map artifact-end         raw:deploy-staged-publication-state-machine  # raw 83

  # nexus-specific extensions (kick + atlas + drill + registry termination events):
  map kick-end             raw:execution-sentinel-result-decoding       # __KICK_RESULT__ <PASS|FAIL> sentinel per raw 80
  map atlas-absorb-end     own:atlas-absorb-mandatory                   # 모든 ω-cycle witness 의 atlas absorb 완료 시점
  map drill-end            raw:design-falsifier-retire-rule             # falsifier outcomes 5/5 평가 후 drill seal
  map registry-rotation-end raw:execution-daemon-singleton-stale-lock-witness  # launchd sweeper rotation

  why kick + atlas-absorb + drill-end + registry-rotation-end 은 nexus-unique termination event. generic mapping 으로 covering 안 되어 명시 — 향후 ω-cycle 이 새 END event 발견하면 이 표에 추가, 그렇지 않으면 매핑된 component-raw 재사용.
  scope all nexus termination scenarios

# Cross-reference:
# hive /.end 의 8개 generic mapping 을 그대로 상속하면서 nexus 4개 (kick/atlas-absorb/drill/registry-rotation)
# 추가. 새 termination event 후보 발견 시:
#   1. 기존 component-raw 재사용 가능? → 매핑만 추가
#   2. 정말 novel? → component-raw 자체를 hive .raw 에 신규 등록 후 .end 에 cross-link

# follow-up (raw 90 compliance ramp, 60d target):
#   1. raw#2 self-format keys whitelist — end-composition / end-event-type-mapping / component-raw / map
#      (hive 가 이미 추가했다면 재사용)
#   2. tool/end_composition_check.hexa — full impl (currently scaffold)
#   3. cross-link: own#1 atlas-absorb-mandatory follow-up 에 "composition role: atlas-absorb-end via .end" 추가
#   4. raw 1 os-lock 확장 — chflags uchg .end
